title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - What's new in the marketplace - week 26
description:
In this video we will have a look at which items are added to the marketplace for MSFS 2020 the pc version. This week several airports have been added including multiple ones in China. Besides this some livery packs are added for the A320 V2. Additionally a new helicopter has been added so if you love flying a helicopter you also have something new to look at, and the good news: a new helipad is also available.
